# TemplateInsertable

**Protocol**

A protocol supporting the custom language model training data result builder.

## Declaration

```swift
protocol TemplateInsertable
```

## Protocol requirements

- **insert(generator:)**

## Result builder support

- **SFCustomLanguageModelData.CompoundTemplate**: A class supporting the custom language model training data result builder. You are not intended to use this directly.
- **DataInsertable**: A protocol supporting the custom language model training data result builder.

## Conforming Types

- SFCustomLanguageModelData.CompoundTemplate
- SFCustomLanguageModelData.TemplatePhraseCountGenerator.Template
